lead_paragraph: Josh Donaldson, Michael Saunders and Josh Thole homered to help R.A. Dickey and the Toronto Blue Jays beat the Tampa Bay Rays 5-3 on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Donaldson Homers as Blue Jays Beat Rays 5-3
